{"tid":1092693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠抽不能算笠……笠水！","createTime":"2019-04-05T05:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T12:02:28.000Z","uid":60658,"like":134,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cd19cd1d50bdca8fb01f4eb67ad970b38d30bab6","tid":1092693,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"世界情色王一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「世清，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「犯法野唔做。」他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又笠水了！」世界情色王睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？宇城飛場都book埋。」世界情色王便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「唔夠抽不能算笠&hellip;&hellip;笠水！&hellip;&hellip;以上係我同佢嘅事，唔關波台事。」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「淆字我唔曉寫」，什麼「宇狗一早歸西啦」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"2e17b98fc5fac8700d0a0e0513916e83caaf620c","tid":1092693,"uid":60658,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecada45798574d96a4c5f4e9851a2567b715032","tid":1092693,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c7a41fcddb0d08fb1a3861b0909cf6563b4ba8","tid":1092693,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fecada45798574d96a4c5f4e9851a2567b715032","tid":1092693,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27186d5552adb03f8cbda79050910e1093e4dc0","tid":1092693,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"世乙己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263963f130025a2964a99bdf13e2d379b84264fa","tid":1092693,"uid":47783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited